# 🛡️ AI Kavach – Real-Time Audio Deepfake & Financial Scam Shield

## Overview

AI Kavach is an AI-powered application designed to detect AI-generated voice deepfakes and identify potential financial scam conversations. The system combines speech processing, deep learning, and a web-based interface to provide real-time analysis of uploaded audio.

---

## Problem Statement

AI-generated voice cloning and financial scams are becoming increasingly common. AI Kavach helps identify suspicious audio by analyzing speech patterns and detecting signs of synthetic or fraudulent content.

---

## Features

- Audio Deepfake Detection
- Financial Scam Analysis
- Multilingual Audio Support
- Real-Time Audio Processing
- Interactive HTML Dashboard
- FastAPI Backend
- Modular AI Pipeline

